			<node ID="ID_333121579" TEXT="First we&#8217;re going to take a look at 3 primary project management metrics: 1. Planned Value (PV) project KPI. This metric is also referred to as Budgeted Cost of Work Scheduled (BCWS). The planned value is the estimated cost for your project activities planned/scheduled as of reporting date." />
