			<node ID="ID_1308935092" TEXT="Project Management Performance Metrics &#8211; Suggested Metrics for Portfolio Performance. Monitoring and Controlling the Project / By Ronda Bowen / Project Management. Project Management Performance Metrics. A metric is defined as something that can gauge the status of a deliverable; aimed as small measurable attributes that have a predictive or " />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_1823147719" LINK="https://www.projectmanager.com/blog/project-performance-metrics" TEXT="A Guide to Project Performance Metrics - ProjectManager.com">
			<node ID="ID_1895872496" TEXT="You can automate much of the process of monitoring project performance by setting up your metrics in your project management software. Then use the dashboard features to report on progress in real-time. ProjectManager.com makes it easy to see the status of your project at any time from anywhere. You&#8217;ll be able to track how well your team is " />
			</node>
