			<node ID="ID_627819133" TEXT="COCOMO II Effort Equation. The COCOMO II model makes its estimates of required effort (measured in Person-Months -- PM) based primarily on your estimate of the software projects size (as measured in thousands of SLOC KSLOC)): Effort = 2.94 * EAF * (KSLOC) E Where EAF Is the Effort Adjustment Factor derived from the Cost Drivers" />
			</node>
