			<node ID="ID_382989012" TEXT="COCOMO II - Constructive Cost Model Model(s) COCOMO COSYSMO COCOMO and COSYSMO COCOMO and COQUALMO Monte Carlo Risk On Off Auto Calculate On Off" />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_1205743717" LINK="https://csse.usc.edu/csse/research/COCOMO_suite/index.html" TEXT="CSSE Website">
			<node ID="ID_1635323431" TEXT="Agile COCOMO&#174; II . The Center continues to research Agile COCOMO&#174; II a cost estimation tool that is based on COCOMO&#174; II.It uses analogy-based estimation to generate accurate results while being very simple to use and easy to learn." />
