			<node ID="ID_780506210" TEXT="COCOMO II is tuned to modern software life cycles. The original COCOMO model has been very successful but it doesnt apply to newer software development practices as well as it does to traditional practices. COCOMO II targets modern software projects and will continue to evolve over the next few years." />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_553696994" LINK="https://csse.usc.edu/csse/research/COCOMOII/cocomo_downloads.htm" TEXT="CSSE Website">
