			<node ID="ID_1221885124" TEXT="COCOMO II has 7 to 17 multiplicative factors that determine the effort required to complete a software project. All cost drivers have qualitative rating levels (extra low to extra high) that express the impact of the driver and a corresponding set of effort multiplier. The nominal level always has an effort multiplier (EM) of 1.00 which" />
			</node>
