			<node ID="ID_299848443" TEXT="COCOMO II only uses size data that influences effort which is new code and code that is copied and modified. For new and reused code a method is used to make them equivalent so they can be rolled up into an aggregate size estimate. The baseline size in COCOMO II is a count of new lines of code." />
			</node>
